Fix compilation error with riscv arch:

|  8:42.65 E [...]/js/src/jit/riscv64/Simulator-riscv64.h:32:4: error: "simulator disabled"
|  8:42.65 E    32 | #  error "simulator disabled"


These files have been heavily refactored by upstream since this release,
and it doesn't apply anymore to the development version, so it cannot be upstreamed.

The latest revision is untested for this bug, but in theory this patch
can be dropped with the next major upgrade.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [see above]
Signed-off-by: Gyorgy Sarvari <skandigraun@gmail.com>

